PATTERN GEARS

pattern_gears recognizes "gears" used where "years" was meant
adjacent letters on the keyboard; one of fadriel's father's recurring slips
context usually makes the intended word clear

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe dyslexic_organ.zc

the 7 properties of pattern_gears:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE zero
6 COUPLING one
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB recognize
scan for "gears" in semantic contexts where "years" is intended

VERB correct
substitute "years" silently when the surrounding sentence indicates the temporal meaning
